quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,29,"Mo a moagye adie, sε mosuro Nyankopͻn a Ɔbεyε mo sononko na W’apepa mo mfomsoͻ afri moso na Ɔde (mo bͻne) akyε mo. Na Nyankopͻn na ͻwͻ adom kεseε paa no"
  8,30,"Kae εberε a boniayεfoͻ no kͻͻ wo tri so apam sε wͻ’de wo bεto afiase, anaasε wͻ’beku wo, anaasε wͻ’betu wo (afri ͻman no mu); wͻ’bͻͻ pͻ paa, na Nyankopͻn nso bͻͻ pͻ, na Nyankopͻn pͻbͻ na εyε pͻbͻ pa kyεn apͻ bͻfoͻ nyinaa"
  8,31,"Sε yεrekenkan Yεn Nsεm no kyerε wͻn a, deε wͻ’ka nesε: “Y’ate, sε yεpε a anka yεbetumi aka deε εte saa. Nokorε sε, woi yε tetefoͻ no anansesεm “"
  8,32,"Kae εbrε a wͻ’kaa sε: “Otumfoͻ Nyankopͻn, sε (Qur’aan) woi yε nokorε a efri Wo nkyεn ampa a, εneε tͻ aboͻ nsuo fri soro gu yεn so, anaasε fa asotwee a εyε ya paa bra yεn so “"
  8,33,"Ԑmma sε Nyankopͻn bεtwe wͻn aso wͻ aberε a wo (Nkͻmhyεni Muhammad) wo wͻ wͻn mu, na εmma nso sε Nyankopͻn bεtwe wͻn aso aberε a wͻ’resrε bͻnefakyε"
  8,34,"Anoyie bεn na wͻn wͻ a enti Nyankopͻn nntwe wͻn aso, aberε a wͻ’resi (amanfoͻ) kwan fri Nyamedan kronkron no ho, aberε nso a εnyε wͻn ne εso hwεfoͻ? Ɛso hwεfoͻ no mmom deε wͻ’ne Nyamesurofoͻ no, nanso wͻn mu dodoͻ no ara nnim"
  8,35,(Abosomsomfoͻ no) asͻreyε wͻ (Ka’aba) Efie no ho ara ne hwerεma bͻ ne nsambͻ. Enti monka (asotwee no) nhwε εnam mo boniayε no ho nti
  8,36,"Nokorε sε, boniayεfoͻ no sεe wͻn sika sεdeε wͻ’besi (amanfoͻ kwan) afri Nyankopͻn kwan no soᴐ. Wͻ’bεkͻ so asεe no, ama ayε brεguo ama wͻn, na yadi wͻn so nkonim. Wͻn a wͻ’yi boniayε no, yεbεboa wͻn ano akͻ Amanehunu gyem"
  8,37,"Sεdeε Nyankopͻn beyiyi abͻneεfoͻ no afri apapafoͻ no mu; na Ɔbεma (yahyehyε) abͻneεfoͻ no ama ebinom adeda ebinom so, aboa wͻn ano de wͻn akͻ Amanehunu gyem. Saa nkorͻfoͻ no ne brεguofoͻ no"